<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=11957&amp;p=140126#p140126"><![CDATA[
Fun little secret I found today.<br /><br />Enter the title screen[1] while holding left+down OR right+down [2], then select Credits. One of two secret messages will be printed before the thanks.<br /><br />[1]: For example by exiting the controller screen.<br />[2]: When the title screen appears you may release the buttons.<br /><br />---<br />March 13 ninja edit:<br /><br /><div class="quotetitle">in <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?p=135000#p135000" class="postlink">this post</a>, tepples wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />There's also some apparently unused code related to the NerdTracker II playback code at $8006, but I have no idea what it's supposed to be doing.<br /></div><br />These Game Genie Codes will turn Solar Wars into a graphic-less sound test mode:<br />UENNXYLK<br />OENNUNSN<br />TEKKLLLA<br /><br />The A button advances to the next track.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=6385">JRoatch</a> — Thu Jan 29, 2015 7:25 pm</p><hr />
